      "content": "i just walked into the kitchen and realized i made two cups of coffee again. by habit. i sat there staring at his empty chair for twenty minutes. the silence in this house is actually deafening. i dont even know why i bother getting up in the morning anymore. everything just feels so heavy and pointless without him.",
