      "content": "free from the need to pretend... i never thought of it like that. but honestly, it just feels like being empty. i look at his things, his clothes still in the closet, and it's like my heart isn't even in my body anymore. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting this. if the pain is just going to be this permanent, what's the point of dragging myself through another day of nothingness? it feels like i'm just stuck in a loop of suffering.",
